vessel-claymore-name = ЗОБ Claymore
vessel-claymore-desc = A full frontal assault ship, made by the Zealots of Balaam in order to enact the will of their prophet. Features a devastating front facing armnament, much to the detriment of everything else. Any mercenary looking to unleash an awesome frontal barrage can use this ship for their own purposes. Has a MIL designation.
